Specific changes:
- Chapter 09 §1 and §4 reframe v0 conformance as a sequence of levels (v1, v1+roles, v1+roles+integrator), with v1 covering the task-store + wire subset only. Removed the 'passes v1 = conformant to chapters 02/04/05/06/07/08' overclaim. Updated §7 and §5 wording too. (Round-1 finding 1.)
- Added test_retry_exhausted_eval_error_terminalization to §E.8 — drives POST /trials/{T}/declare-eval-error and asserts trial.status flips starting → eval_error atomically with the trial.eval_errored event. (Round-1 finding 2.)
