- Reference adapter now passes --subscribe-timeout 2.0 so the timeout-path test runs in 2-3 seconds instead of 30s; added a §D paragraph explaining the override is spec-conforming since chapter 7 §6.2 makes 30s a SHOULD. (Round-1 residual risk 1.)

