    13	is a `README.md` stub reserving the location.
    14	
    15	This plan delivers exactly what chunk 11a + 11b says it should:
    16	
    17	1. The harness — pytest-driven, IUT-adapter-shaped.
    18	2. The first scenarios — task lifecycle, claim-token semantics,
    19	   transactional event invariant including all chapter-05 §2.2
