    89	### In scope (this chunk)
    90	
    91	1. **Harness infrastructure** under [`conformance/harness/`](../../conformance/harness/):
    92	   - `IutAdapter` Protocol — start a subject, return a handle that
    93	     exposes the wire-protocol base URL and any auth material the
