   219	## Design
   220	
   221	### A. Layout
   222	
   223	```text
   224	conformance/
   225	├── README.md                      # Updated: "v1 ships with chunk 11a+11b"
   226	├── pyproject.toml                 # NEW — separate uv workspace member
   227	├── conftest.py                    # imports harness.plugin
