   560	
   561	| Test | Asserts | Citation |
   562	|---|---|---|
   563	| `test_reclaim_operator_from_claimed` | Operator reclaim from claimed: 200; back to pending; claim cleared; `task.reclaimed` event with `cause=operator`. | 04 §5.1, §5.2 |
   564	| `test_reclaim_operator_from_submitted` | Same for submitted. | 04 §5.1 |
   565	| `test_reclaim_expired_from_claimed` | Claim with `expires_at` in the past, then reclaim with `cause=expired`: 200. | 04 §5.1 |
   566	| `test_reclaim_expired_against_submitted_rejected` | Cannot apply automatic reclaim to submitted (rejected with 409). | 04 §5.1 |
   567	| `test_implement_reclaim_sets_starting_trial_to_error` | Implement reclaim after `create_trial(status="starting")`: trial flips to `error` atomically with the reclaim. Both `task.reclaimed` and `trial.errored` events appear in the log. | 04 §5.4; 05 §2.2 |
