   638	#### E.8 Composite commits (`test_composite_commits.py`)
   639	
   640	Per chapter 05 §2.2, six composite-commit cases. Each test:
   641	
   642	- Drives the composite operation through the wire binding,
   643	- Reads the event log,
   644	- Asserts both component events are present (no partial visibility),
