   721	are pinned by a normative MUST (codex review round 0 finding #2).
   722	
   723	#### E.14 Integrate idempotency (`test_integrate_idempotency.py`)
   724	
   725	The fixture model is **simplified** from the pre-review draft per
   726	codex review round 0 finding #8: instead of driving plan → implement →
   727	evaluate to produce a real `success` trial, the test seeds the trial
   728	directly through the storage endpoints in chapter 07 §3-4. The wire
   729	endpoint's normative contract (chapter 07 §5) treats `trial_commit_sha`
   730	as a "well-formed commit SHA" — only the regex shape is checked at the
   731	task-store layer. Reachability is the integrator's MUST (chapter 06
   732	§2), not the task store's. The v1 test uses placeholder 40-hex SHAs.
   733	
   734	| Test | Asserts | Citation |
   735	|---|---|---|
   736	| `test_first_integrate_returns_200_emits_event` | First call with `trial_commit_sha=<40-hex>` returns 200; one `trial.integrated` event appears. | 07 §5 |
   737	| `test_same_value_idempotency` | Second call with the same SHA returns 200; still exactly one `trial.integrated` event. | 07 §5 |
   738	| `test_different_sha_returns_409` | Second call with a different SHA returns 409 `eden://error/invalid-precondition`; stored value unchanged. | 07 §5 |
   739	| `test_integrate_against_non_success_trial_returns_409` | Trial with `status != "success"` rejects integrate with `invalid-precondition`. | 07 §5 |
   740	
   741	The setup helper (`integrate_test_trial_factory`):
   742	
   743	1. `POST /v0/experiments/{E}/proposals` with `state=drafting`,
   744	   `parent_commits=["0"*40]`, `slug="test"`, `priority=0.5`.
   745	2. `POST /v0/experiments/{E}/proposals/{P}/mark-ready`.
   746	3. `POST /v0/experiments/{E}/trials` with `proposal_id=P`,
   747	   `commit_sha="1"*40`, `status=starting`.
   748	4. `POST /v0/experiments/{E}/tasks` for `evaluate` referencing trial.
   749	5. Claim → submit `status=success` with valid metrics → accept.
   750	6. Integrate against the now-`success` trial.
   751	
   752	Steps 1-5 use only chapter-07 endpoints. No git operations, no
   753	worker-host coordination. This keeps 11a + 11b's scope clean of
   754	chapter-03 role semantics.
